    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/22d4217b87918ad67b30343ddc7ceaac.poster.avif?t=1766430998\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/22d4217b87918ad67b30343ddc7ceaac.webm?t=1766430998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/22d4217b87918ad67b30343ddc7ceaac.mp4?t=1766430998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在2400年，地球科学家发现了「诸神星球」—— 这些世界遍地都是不可思议的神圣宝藏。但每个星球都由强大的守护之神守护着。只有最勇敢的人敢加入陆战队，进行一次短暂而危险的登陆任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/4620b01b9ebeffc7758cf352ddc488f7.avif?t=1766430998\" width=800 height=128 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/6492c0839c08cae4cf7e4e68e881edfc.poster.avif?t=1766430998\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/6492c0839c08cae4cf7e4e68e881edfc.webm?t=1766430998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/6492c0839c08cae4cf7e4e68e881edfc.mp4?t=1766430998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>陆战队的目标：</strong><br>尽可能收集更多的神圣宝藏，抵御来自神明的无情攻击——包括怪物大军、陷阱和毁灭性的灾难，并成功从星球上撤离。<br><br><strong>神明的目标：</strong><br>通过战略性地选择最佳法术，明智地管理法力、布置陷阱、召唤生物和操控元素，消灭陆战队。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/a6698dd3815c2555e18f0dff5bd41f27.avif?t=1766430998\" width=800 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/fa2442a1eee42292df4cfe036ef1eeb5.webp?t=1766430998\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>召唤僵尸</strong> — 攻击附近的陆战队员。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/3b5b72475438d54f4332cf795b2d6b03.webp?t=1766430998\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>灵能风暴</strong> — 在区域内造成闪电伤害。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/d5f905e2b7489c836a70b6c80369b20c.webp?t=1766430998\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>分身幻象</strong> — 制造欺骗性的复制品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/7b551eed8a54c4047df06595af552473.webp?t=1766430998\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>火球术</strong> — 短暂延迟后造成大量伤害。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/24b13c9b2dc53c10e6cd57feebd29b31.webp?t=1766430998\" width=24 height=24 /></span> <strong>石墙屏障</strong> — 在选定位置创造一道墙壁。<br><br><strong>以及更多！</strong><br><i>每种法术都能改变战局— 根据你的游戏风格调整战术！</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209950/extras/7251ac1a1509542272558410b7922719.avif?t=1766430998\" width=800 height=128 /></span><br><br><strong>每个星球都独特且充满秘密：</strong><br>• 火星荒原<br>• 未来之城<br>• 丛林迷宫<br>• 冰霜要塞<br>• 废弃文明<br><br><strong>选择你的神明：</strong><br>宙斯、恶魔之王、阿纳尔·德瑞姆斯 (Anar Dreams)<br><br><strong>选择你的陆战队员：</strong><br>防御者、狙击手、医疗兵或工程师<br><br><strong>多种游戏模式：</strong><br>经典非对称模式（4对1）— 神明对抗陆战队。<br>PvP、PvE、合作模式以及与朋友或AI的混合模式（最多8名玩家）。",
